# Florsovivexa Feature Modules

## Photo Editor Module
- Screen for editing photos with stickers and cropping functionality
- Allows adding emojis/stickers that can be moved, scaled, and rotated
- Saves edited photos to the device gallery

## Journal Module ("好事发生")
- Records positive events and good news
- Supports tagging entries with categories (#成就, #小确幸, etc.)
- Displays entries in a timeline format

## Tea Tracker Module ("奶茶记")
- Records bubble tea/coffee consumption
- Tracks spending, ratings, and consumption statistics
- Generates monthly reports on consumption and spending

## Settings Module
- Theme switching (dark/light)
- Notification preferences
- User profile management (no login required)